Price and distributions
as of 07/28/2017





Market priceThe price at which a security trades in the secondary market. The market price is determined by the midpoint between the bid and asked prices as of the closing time of the New York Stock Exchange (typically 4 p.m., Eastern time) on business days.
Change $/%



